  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育系统设计一个完整的LMS门户到课堂服务的流程图，重点是处理成绩同步和内容分发的决策逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我先确认一下整体结构：从LMS门户开始，然后连接到课堂服务，中间会有多个决策点判断是否需要同步成绩，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。而且成绩同步节点本身也是个决策点，根据同步结果可能会走不同的分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出起始节点A作为LMS门户，然后直接连到课堂服务节点B。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "B之后需要第一个判断节点，检查课堂服务状态。这个菱形节点C如果判断为否，应该直接结束流程并标记错误状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加菱形判断节点C，No分支指向错误结束节点D，用红色填充。Yes分支继续往下走。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "D的红色标记很好。Yes分支回到LMS门户节点E，这里需要第二次判断用户权限。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "权限判断节点F如果为否，也是错误结束吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，无权限直接结束到G，同样标红。有权限才进入成绩同步的判断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加了权限判断节点F，No分支到红色节点G，Yes分支连接到成绩同步判断节点H。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "成绩同步节点H如果判断不需要同步，直接结束到I标红；需要同步则执行同步服务J。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成H节点的两个分支：No到红色节点I，Yes到GradeSync服务节点J。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "J之后要连接内容分发网络K，这是为了加载课程资源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
